rules.name: myRule_12
rules.label: Set Non AMS Auto Renewal Fields

Flow.description: Used to set opportunity fields used for CPQ and/or Billing

formulas.name: formula_myRule_12

value.stringValue: AND( Isnew(), [Opportunity].SBQQ__Renewal__c = TRUE, AND( [Opportunity].SBQQSC__RenewedServiceContract__r.Auto_Renew__c = TRUE, OR( [Opportunity].SBQQSC__RenewedServiceContract__r.SBQQSC__Opportunity__r.RecordType.DeveloperName = "AMS_Auto_Renewal", [Opportunity].SBQQSC__RenewedServiceContract__r.SBQQSC__Opportunity__r.RecordType.DeveloperName = "Application_Managed_Services" ) ) )

formulas.name: formula_myRule_15
formulas.expression: AND( Isnew(), {!myVariable_current.SBQQ__Renewal__c} = TRUE, AND( {!myVariable_current.SBQQSC__RenewedServiceContract__r.Auto_Renew__c} = TRUE, OR( {!myVariable_current.SBQQSC__RenewedServiceContract__r.SBQQSC__Opportunity__r.RecordType.DeveloperName} = "AMS_Auto_Renewal", {!myVariable_current.SBQQSC__RenewedServiceContract__r.SBQQSC__Opportunity__r.RecordType.DeveloperName} = "Application_Managed_Services" ) ) )
